A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Brookwood High School girls swim and dive team for winning the 2025
2 GHSA Class 6A State Swimming and Diving Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Brookwood High School girls swim and dive team has established and
4 maintained a proud tradition of excellence with equal emphasis on character and academics;
5 and
6 WHEREAS, excellent performance, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made
7 this team a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its
8 remarkable 2025 campaign, the team captured its second consecutive state title with a
9 decisive 427-269 victory over runner-up Harrison; and
10 WHEREAS, the team was led by Nicole Amike, who earned individual state titles in the
11 50-yard and 100-yard freestyles as well as contributed to the winning 200-yard freestyle
12 relay team along with Sophie Hamilton, Hailey Dopson, and Amelia Moore; and
13 WHEREAS, as additional testament to the team's exemplary performance, Hailey Dopson
14 also secured an individual state title in the 100-yard backstroke; and
